text.tspan: Blue 2 - #1B3B56 - Used for hover state - icons
White - #FFFFFF - Used for all text & close and minimize glyphs
When launcher is docked to the top of the screen, it is as wide as the screen itself
When launcher is docked to the side
of the screen, it is as tall as the screen
The search bar + search icon sit midway between the watchlist icon and the docking icons.
The distance between the search bar and the other elements can vary depending on screen size.
All other icons have a bounding box of 60px by 60 px.
Active - Teal icon, transparent binding box
Inactive - Blue 1 icon, transparent binding box
